divs: sighting detailshttp:\\www.ufocasebook.com\news.html i filed a report with ufo casebook here is the link. i fed the cats in the barn and when i was down i walked outside to go to the house. i'm not sure of the time, i fed the cats after coming home from night church which is at 4pm, church usually gets out at 5:30. the last time i looked at a clock was on the way home and it was 5:45, church is about 10-15 minutes away from home. i orignally said the time was between 5:30-6:00p, but after searching the sky the next night i'd say the time was more between 6:30-7:00pm. i walked out of the barn, and the sky was clear i looked up at the stars. the barn is to the west of the house and the door i exited from the barn was on the north side. above me and to the left (west) was a jet flying in the air, i saw the blinking lights and trail it left so i knew it was a jet. directly above me i saw 3 lights in a triangle, two white lights and a red one in the middle but toward the front and it flew over me heading in a north direction. it was windy outside so i didn't hear any noise. at first i thought it was just an airplane and went inside, but later saw pictures from ufo casebook of another case which fit exactly what i saw. the picture i'm attaching is from another case, but is what i saw.

Summary: I came out of the barn and looked overhead and lit flew over me.
